room_title: Escape room "Hole in the Wall" by Hint Hunter Puzzle Rooms in Biloxi

room_description: You two are part of the Hint Hunter Hooligans, one of the most wanted outlaw gangs in the Wild West. Now locked up in the county jail, you have to work together and search for clues left by the previous prisoners. You have 30 minutes to assemble the dynamite and blow your way out!
